{
  "stem": "10549.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I got the news that some people who knew something about her, that she was killed in the city where, when they're, where liquidating the Jewish population of that city, that she got killed in that city.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Borisoff.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was more to the Russian border on the-- it was still on the Polish side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed for around three, four months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father decided-- he had some jewelry with him, and he tried to make a, a living.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how we-- he couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we tried to go to a larger city, you know, in order to maybe sell some of his belongings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he went to city of Cracow-- 'Cracoff' Polish-- in 'Cracoff'.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it's Cracow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was supposed to come back, but he never came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After three, four weeks I didn't hear from him, so I decide-- I was smuggling myself on the train that time, and I decided to go to the same city.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I found out that, unfortunately, he was picked up on a raid, because the Germans used to make raids on the Jewish sections.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Certain sections they made the raids, and they went from house to house, and they used to confiscate a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and they caught my father, also on that raid, with that jewelry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They confiscate the jewelry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they, they locked him in, in a, in a prison.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's how I found out that he was in a prison.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I tried to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] do all my best in order to release him from the prison, but I was not successful.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one day-- my father was a very-- his hobby used to be listen to operas.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
